dc_title_s: Mappe - monde: pour la geographie de M.M. Achille Meissas et A. Michelot; dressée par Charle géographe.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Shows international boundaries, major rivers and mountains. Gravé par Moisy. 1 map: col. 28 x 52 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
